Question:
Given 3 numbers A, B and C. Find the greatest number among them.

Solution:
class Solution {
    int greatestOfThree(int A, int B, int C) {
      if(A>B&&A>C)
      return A;
      else if(B>A&&B>C)
      return B;
      else return C;
      
    }
}

Explaination: Using flow control statements, compare the values of the given numbers and return the greater value.
